ascend_skill.desc:
When using a skill, spend all Childish Heart stacks to increase party's Attack by 8% for each Childish Heart stack spent for 2 turns. Childish Heart stacks up to 5 times.
 When Haruna gains Childish Heart stacks, gain the same number of Mystery stacks. Mystery stacks are lost when Haruna uses a Highlight or after 2 turns, and stack up to 5 times.
ascend_skill.name: Off to Treasure Hunt

ascend_skill.desc:
When an ally deals damage with a skill, increase Haruna's Attack by 20%. Stacks up to 3 times. This effect ends when Haruna uses a skill.
Also, when Haruna's Attack is increased 2 times, increase party's damage by 15% for 1 turn.
ascend_skill.name: Let's Go, Everyone!

ascend_skill.desc:
Let's Hold Hands increases the chance of gaining Childish Heart by 20%.
When using Courageous Campaign and Childish Heart stacks are at maximum, increase Attack and critical damage by 24% for 2 turns.
ascend_skill.name: Here to Help

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Courageous Campaign and Thief Tactics by 3.
ascend_skill.name: Still Growing

ascend_skill.desc: Highlight Enhanced: Extend damage increase duration by 2 turns.
ascend_skill.name: Give It to Them

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Surprise Squad and Ready for Adventure by 3.
ascend_skill.name: A Little Maintenance

ascend_skill.desc:
When Childish Heart reaches 5 stacks, gain Curiosity.
Curiosity: When Haruna deals damage with a skill, increase damage by 75%. This effect ends after dealing skill damage to foes.
ascend_skill.name: Puzzle Solver

highlight_skill.desc: Deal Psychokinesis damage to 1 foe equal to 366.0%/403.5%/388.5%/426.0% of Attack. Increase party's damage by 7.8%/8.6%/8.3%/9.1% for each stack of Mystery for 1 turn.
highlight_skill.name: Highlight

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Psychokinesis damage to 1 foe equal to 146.4%/161.4%/155.4%/170.4% of Attack, and grant Affection to party for 1 turn.
Affection: When dealing damage with a skill, grant Haruna 1 Childish Heart stack.
normal_skill.name: Surprise Squad

normal_skill.desc:
Increase party's healing received and shield received by 17.6%/19.4%/18.6%/20.4%, and Defense by 34.2%/37.7%/36.3%/39.8% for 2 turns.
If Haruna does not have Childish Heart, gain 2 Childish Heart stacks.
normal_skill.name: Ready for Adventure

normal_skill.desc:
This skill requires Childish Heart.
When used with Childish Heart, increase party's Attack by 10% for 2 turns.
At 2 or more stacks of Childish Heart, also increase party's damage by 1% for every 100 of Haruna's Attack, up to 48.8%/53.8%/51.8%/56.8%.
normal_skill.name: Courageous Campaign

passive_skill.desc: Each time an ally with Affection deals damage, 40.0% chance to gain 1 Childish Heart stack.
passive_skill.name: Let's Hold Hands

passive_skill.desc: When spending 3 or more Childish Heart stacks at once, increase effects of Off to Treasure Hunt by 24.0% more.
passive_skill.name: Safety in Numbers
